Subject Re Need advice for riding with someone on pillion From Stafford Vax Winona MSUS Edu John Stafford In article MELLON A Ted Lemon writes On a long ride with my ex girlfriend Nancy, I would notice her drifting off every so often I swore off taking passengers over ten years ago, but I recall Sturgis, getting some strange looks because my passenger was reading a book She was so engrossed that she didn't even notice when we hit a roadkill to make the hit of the day with the riders behind us John Stafford Minnesota State University Winona All standard disclaimers apply